data.description: Coming Soon - Looking for that home in the country?  Here is a 3 bedroom home with a walkout basement and a pole barn on 4.27 acres outside of Sparta IL.  The inside of this home recently had a recent update where they took out the wall between the kitchen and living room and at the stairs giving an open concept with a modern rustic country feel.  The convenient main level laundry and the sun porch make for some great features. Plus there is a full walk out basement that would be easy to finish for some extra space.  Already a bathroom on the basement level.
